                    <span>After reading this biography of him, I had so much more knowledge of him that I didn't have before. There is more to his life than what most people think. A must read for jazz/Coltrane fans! A lot of musical analysis, too.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">Outstanding Biography!</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
                      <span>5</span>
