                    <span>This book has everything; the most thorough life biography, yet, and a musician's analysis of Trane's important works, with loads of playable examples. Occasionally the author toots his horn a bit much, but he knows what he's talking about.<p>All in all, a fascinating read into Trane's life and music.</span>
                  
              
